These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, nectarine
1. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Food   | kiwi | nectarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, adventure
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, soul
1. the fan of classical is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | soul | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-4::.
